    think='Let me check more things. I need to see the Dart generated model to u
nderstand the current state, and also check if there are any tests for the mobil
e side. Let me also check if the `last_login_at` field is mentioned anywhere in 
the code.\n\nAlso, let me look at the `pubspec.yaml` changes and the `auth.yaml`
