le/lib/models/generated/auth/` are out of sync with the runtime API. `check-cont
ract-sync` would fail.\n\n4. **❌ Missing `last_login_at`**: The PRD US-AUTH-2 r
equires updating `users.last_login_at` on successful login. The `UserEntity`, mi
gration, and `AuthService.login()` do not implement this.\n\n5. **❌ BDD step de
