t entirely `TODO` comments with no real implementation. This violates the testin
g.md requirement that BDD tests should be executable.\n\n6. **❌ No Mobile unit/
widget tests**: There are no Flutter tests (`*_test.dart`) for `AuthBloc`, `Logi
nPage`, `AuthInterceptor`, or `SecureStorage`. The generated openapi tests exist
