S rate limiting (1 min / 1 req, 1 hour / 5 req). Not implemented.\n\n8. **❌ `se
edSmsCode` dev helper unreachable**: `AuthService.seedSmsCode()` exists but no c
ontroller endpoint exposes it, making BDD/manual dev testing impossible without 
